@startuml
title Enterprise AI-Buildable Specification Process - Swimlane by Role

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam activity {
  BorderColor #444444
  BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF8E1
  DiamondBorderColor #B26A00
  StartColor #2E7D32
  EndColor #2E7D32
  BarColor #666666
  ArrowColor #444444
}

|Product Manager|
start
:Define product purpose;
:Draft constitution;
:Define business goals and requirements;
:Prioritize delivery phases;

|Architect|
:Refine constitution into system boundaries;
:Define architecture (C4);
:Define domain model;
:Define integration contracts;
:Define execution specification pack;

|Designer|
:Define UX information architecture;
:Define UX style guide;
:Define enterprise design system;
:Define screen contracts;
:Define component contracts;

|Product Manager|
:Define decision tables and business rules;
:Define acceptance criteria;
:Approve scope for implementation;

|Architect|
:Define API contracts;
:Define event model;
:Define state transition matrix;
:Define permission and concurrency model;

|Designer|
:Validate UX consistency across all screens;
:Validate that workflows, tables, and drill-downs are coherent;

|Product Manager|
if (Specification sufficiently complete?) then (yes)
  |AI Coding Agent|
  :Generate application structure;
  :Generate backend services;
  :Generate frontend screens and components;
  :Generate integration adapters;
  :Generate tests;
  
  |Architect|
  :Review technical correctness;
  :Review architecture fidelity;
  
  |Designer|
  :Review UX fidelity;
  :Review design system compliance;
  
  |Product Manager|
  :Review business workflow correctness;
  
  if (Defects, ambiguity, or drift found?) then (yes)
    :Route issues back to responsible role;
    |Architect|
    :Refine technical specs as needed;
    |Designer|
    :Refine UX / design specs as needed;
    |Product Manager|
    :Refine requirements / rules as needed;
    |AI Coding Agent|
    :Regenerate affected implementation;
  else (no)
    |Product Manager|
    :Approve implementation baseline;
    stop
  endif
else (no)
  :Identify missing specification artifacts;
  |Architect|
  :Close architecture / data / API gaps;
  |Designer|
  :Close UX / screen / component gaps;
  |Product Manager|
  :Close requirement / rule / acceptance gaps;
  --> :Define business goals and requirements;
endif

@enduml